version_description:
We’ve upgraded our app’s design, navigation and features to give you a better banking experience.

New features:
* Faster login, with one-step authentication and Touch ID (Touch ID is available if supported by your device and after your first login)
* Optimized layout for iPad
* Launch a keypad to easily fill in all number fields
* Account balances show immediately upon login
* Scroll to see continuous account history
* View running account balances
* Improved ATM/branch locator
* Search deposit transactions
* Easier to contact KeyPoint
* Apple Watch app

Look for more enhancements in the future!
Fixed automatic check capture on iOS 10.2

– Credit Card: You will be able to view transaction history, search for transactions, view your available credit, perform cash advances, and view your last statement.
– Card Alerts: Set up alerts to keep informed on the use of your debit or credit card.
– Credit Score: Check your latest FICO® score anytime for free.
– Modern Design: Redesigned screens in Account, Move Money and some Menus.
– Miscellaneous Enhancements.
Navigation improvements: External transfers can now be found under Move Money > Send Money
Added credit card cash advances, minor bug fixes and other enhancements.

- Enhanced Digital Applications for new accounts and loans
- Bug fixes
